Items.c: <[>是了,雖說夏侯掌門摔下山谷的原因是與我爭鬥,定不可能是他人陰謀。<]>
Items.mt: <[>Yes, although the reason why the Sect Leader Xiahou fell down the valley was because of the struggle with me, it is certainly possible that it was a conspiracy of others. <]>

Items.r: 【是了，虽说夏侯掌门摔下山谷的原因是与我争斗，定不可能是他人阴谋。】
